<h2>Chapter 6: Reviews, Ratings, and Reputation on Apple Maps &#123;#chapter-6&#125;</h2>
<p>Apple Maps does not collect its own reviews. Your reputation on Apple Maps depends entirely on third-party review platforms.</p>
<p>This makes review management across multiple platforms essential for Apple Maps SEO success.</p>
<h3>Where Apple Maps Gets Its Reviews</h3>
<p>Apple Maps aggregates reviews from these primary sources:</p>
